item.title: These 5 Black Friday robot vacuum deals prove you don't need to spend top dollar for automated cleaning
item.description: Amazon’s Black Friday sale has seen some premium robot vacuum cleaners drop to their lowest prices yet, including top models from Ecovacs, Roborock and Dreame.

item.title: TikTok now lets you choose how much AI-generated content you want to see
item.description: With the new AI-generated content control, users who want to see less of this sort of content can dial things down, while those who enjoy it can choose to see more of it.

item.title: Emm raises $9M seed to create one of the world’s first ‘smart’ menstrual cups
item.description: On Wednesday, Emm, based in the UK, announced a $9 million seed (£6.8 million) round led by Lunar Ventures as it prepares to officially launch the smart menstrual cup in 2026.

item.title: The Ninja Café Luxe espresso machine drops to an all time Aussie low for Black Friday – grab one now from AU$629
item.description: The Ninja Luxe Café Premier espresso machine caused quite the stir when it launched in Australia – it's now available for its lowest price yet in the Black Friday sales.

item.title: Black Friday deals in Australia are now live – I've found the 100+ best offers on phones, laptops, TVs, appliances and more
item.description: Black Friday 2025 is on November 28, but several retailers have kicked off their official sales. We've got handpicked and highly recommended tech deals right here to make shopping easier.
